''Today is Thursday'', the 5th of March.
Everything is covered in snow, but it's getting warmer and I guess it'll all be gone in a couple of days.

It was floor exercises during PE today, |dp>[(link-goto: "everyone", "Dramatis Personae")] thinks they're girly. And it's true: the only ones who are reasonably good at them are girls. Some girls, anyway. And even those would never admit they like it. 

Will they one day turn on the heating in the gymnastics hall? We were all shivering in the cold as we queued, talking to pass the time. It got quieter and quieter as I got closer towards the exercise mats. Then it was my turn.

|c1>[I tried for a series of cartwheels, as best I could...<br>]\
|c2>[I did a jump roll and a couple of sommersaults...<br>]\
|c3>[]\
|c4>[]
